      <li style="list-style-type:none; padding-left:20px;">Dr. Elbert L. McCreery, Vice President &amp; Dean (no President) <em style="font-size:10px; color:#666;"> 1938-40</em></li> 
      <li style="list-style-type:none; font-weight: bold;">Dr. Wallace L. Emerson <em style="font-size:10px; color:#666;">1940-46</em></li> 
      <li style="list-style-type:none; padding-left:20px;">Dr. Elbert L. McCreery, Interim <em style="font-size:10px; color:#666;">1946-47</em></li> 
      <li style="list-style-type:none; padding-left:20px;">Interim Committee <em style="font-size:10px; color:#666;">1947-48</em></li> 
      <li style="list-style-type:none; font-weight: bold;">Dr. James Forrester <em style="font-size:10px; color:#666;">1948-50</em></li> 
