      <li style="list-style-type:none; font-weight: bold;">Dr. Lyle C. Hillegas <em style="font-size:10px; color:#666;">1972-75</em></li> 
      <li style="list-style-type:none; padding-left:20px;">Dr. Ernest Ettlich, Interim <em style="font-size:10px; color:#666;">1975-76</em></li> 
