       </div> 
       <div style="width:375px; float:left;padding-left:25px;">
        <p><em>Bible Missionary Institute</em> founded and it met in First Fundamental Church in Los Angeles on Alvardo Street.</p>
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div> 
       <div style="width:75px; float:left;">
